Hello, friends!
@Andy | Eco  @Henry  |  Eco , I hope you guys will love that stickers and use it. I tried to do my best.

Idea :Math: 
I really like funny stickers with different world leaders in telegram. I decided why not do something interesting and original with Andy and Henry for eco-mmunity :eco_heart: .
Henry @Henry  |  Eco , I'm sorry, there aren't many photos of you on the Internet, so there aren't as many stickers as I'd like either. Maybe you can share 1-2 photo so I can do better.

The process of work :moneyprinter: 
In order to make the stickers more realistic, you had to find photos with different emotions. It's not so easy. So, i had gone to YouTube. I typed the search query "Andy Bromberg" and watched all the videos. While watching, I took screenshots with certain emotions. This process turned out to be long, but at the same time exciting and fun.
Next, I selected those screenshots that are better suited for a specific emotion. And only then the stickers were made from remaining screenshots. (Example https://i.imgur.com/79d3Qb5.jpg )

I hope it turned out fun :elon: , no one is offended and we will all use them :eco_thumbs_up: . I will use exactly :eco_callme: 
Please let me know if you want see little bit more
